shots.title: Primitive Sun Final (Cool Variant)
shots.description:
I tweaked my final version of my "Primitive Sun" to make a "cooler" color palette variant. Why not?! Both versions will be up on my site within a few days but the original can be found here

http://gavintdesign.com/65618/3649340/home/primitive-sun

shots.title: Pixel Map of Downtown SLC
shots.description:
Spent this ENTIRE week working on this highly inaccurate map of Salt Lake for a conference thing. Attached is the whole map with before and after of vector to pixel.

This is my first time doing pixel art as an adult, so any advice or ideas are welcome.
